NBA FINALS: MAVERICKS v HEAT
June 11, 2011
Mario Chalmers
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT









   MARIO CHALMERS: It's a desperate game for us. It's a game that -- it's a must-win for us. Down 3-2. Battling a good team. 

 Q. Who are the leaders that are coming out of the locker room right now on the court as well? 
 MARIO CHALMERS: Everybody is. Everybody has to understand. Everybody has to get on the same page and know what you're doing. 

 Q. Is it a helpless feeling on the bench, as a point guard saying I need to help this team that's struggling? 
 MARIO CHALMERS: It is. (Indiscernible). Hopefully get out there and if there's something I see on the court, I'm going to do it. 





